name: Japanese New Year
description:
Since I have stared minting NFTs on HEN I have had much support from the Asian population, particularly from Japanese collectors and artist.  I wanted to do this 'shout out' to those supporters with this Japanese themed new year NFT.  

I am minting this for the #HENjackpot "Rocking New Year JACKPOT" event hosted by @rblbab @TerosEso @brainksy @Erythric and @ninacrypto2, who is one of the above mentioned supporters.  THANK YOU! 

This is a hand drawn project using markers and was digitally edited for minting.
